ance from\nknown tax evaders. We thus obtain a list of highly suspicious contributors\nsorted by the amount of evaded tax, valuable information for the authorities to\nfurther investigate illegal tax activity in Mexico. With our methods, we\nestimate previously undetected tax evasion in the order of \\$10 billion USD per\nyear by about 10 thousand contributors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 24 Apr 2021 15:21:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-28"}
